title: 3 layer film blowing extruder machine US-3SJ-50
title_uz: 3 qavatli polietilen plyonka ishlab chiqaruvchi ekstruder US-3SJ-50
title_en: 3 layer film blowing extruder machine US-3SJ-50
short_description: With a maximum production speed of 120 kg per hour, this US-3SJ-50 extruder is capable of producing polyethylene film from 800 mm to 1200 mm wide. The average power consumption of the equipment is 80 kW. The size of the extruder is 9.5*4.5*7.5 m. Other models of this equipment are shown in the description, and they differ in price and parameters.
short_description_uz: Maksimal ishlab chiqarish tezligi soatiga 120 kg ni tashkil etuvchi ushbu US-3SJ-50 ekstruder, kengligi 800 mm dan 1200 mm gacha bo'lgan polietilen plyonka ishlab chiqarish imkoniyatiga ega. Uskunaning o'rtacha quvvat sarfi 80 kW ni tashkil qiladi. Ekstruder o'lchami 9.5*4.5*7.5 m dan iborat. Tavsifda bu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan va ular narx, hamda parametrlarda bir-biridan farq qiladi.
short_description_ru: При максимальной производительности 120 кг в час этот US-3SJ-50 экструдер способен производить полиэтиленовую пленку шириной от 800 мм до 1200 мм. Средняя потребляемая мощность оборудования составляет 80 кВт. Размер экструдера 9,5*4,5*7,5 м. Другие модели данного оборудования представлены в описании и отличаются по цене и параметрам.

long_description:
With a maximum production speed of 120 kg per hour, this US-3SJ-50 extruder is capable of producing polyethylene film from 800 mm to 1200 mm wide. The average power consumption of the equipment is 80 kW. The size of the extruder is 9.5*4.5*7.5 m. Other models of this equipment are shown in the description, and they differ in price and parameters.
